images.alt: A humorous, ultra-detailed photorealistic scene of a worn, scuffed humanoid household robot wearing a blue cleaning smock and yellow rubber gloves, trying to wash a furious, soaking-wet tabby cat in a white bathtub. The robot is holding a handheld shower sprayer above the cat while steadying it with the other hand. The cat is mid-hiss with mouth wide open, ears flattened, claws out, splashing water everywhere, extremely angry and dramatic. The bathtub is overflowing with foamy bubbles and splashing water. The robot shows visible wear and tear: scratched paint, chipped armor panels, dirt, grime, and scuff marks on its arms and body. Bathroom setting, modern and clean, soft neutral colors, shelves with bottles in the background. Water droplets frozen in motion, dynamic action, cinematic lighting. Ultra-realistic fur, metal, and water textures. Shallow depth of field, 35mm lens look, professional photography, high detail, high realism, whimsical and chaotic tone, vertical portrait orientation.
